<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Attendance anomaly alert</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; background:#f6f8fa; margin:0; padding:24px; color:#1f2937;">
  <img src="{{brand.emailHeader}}" alt="ManekHR" style="max-width:240px;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto 16px;border:0;outline:none;text-decoration:none;" />
  <div style="max-width:560px; margin:0 auto; background:#ffffff; border-radius:8px; padding:24px; border:1px solid #e5e7eb;">
    <p style="margin:0 0 8px 0; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; color:#6b7280; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.05em;">Severity: {{severity}}</p>
    <h2 style="margin:0 0 4px 0; font-size:18px; color:#111827;">{{title}}</h2>
    <p style="margin:0 0 16px 0; color:#6b7280; font-size:13px;">Rule: <code style="background:#f3f4f6; padding:2px 6px; border-radius:4px;">{{ruleType}}</code></p>
    <p style="margin:0 0 12px 0; font-size:14px; line-height:1.5; color:#374151;">Hi {{recipientName}},</p>
    <p style="margin:0 0 20px 0; font-size:14px; line-height:1.6; color:#374151;">{{detail}}</p>
    <p style="margin:0 0 24px 0;">
      <a href="{{feedUrl}}" style="display:inline-block; padding:10px 18px; background:#111827; color:#ffffff; text-decoration:none; border-radius:6px; font-size:14px; font-weight:500;">Review anomaly feed</a>
    </p>
    <hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb; margin:16px 0;">
    <p style="margin:0; font-size:12px; color:#9ca3af; line-height:1.5;">This alert was sent because you manage attendance devices for this workspace. To stop receiving anomaly emails, ask an admin to toggle the rule in Attendance &rarr; Settings &rarr; Anomaly rules.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
